Required for startup:
---------------------

1.	New entity coding system

2.	Characters belonging to new players should be invisible for
	the first five turns, unless they perform a prominent action.

	"A new faction cannot be seen by other players for 5 turns unless it
	 interacts with another unit.  Upon interaction, the unit initiating
	 the interaction becomes visible to other units in the area.  At the
	 end of 5 turns, all units in the new faction become visible.
	 Interaction includes combat, trading, or any other action that
	 involves another unit."

