Must create more of this kind of feeling:

  "--gate crystal-- Just found a gate crystal!!! Now that is a really nice
   idea, having a very small chance of finding very rare items when mining.
   Kind of makes up for all that poisonous gas and cave ins my miners have
   endured. Are the hooks for this gate crystal in place yet? I haven't seen
   anything about it in any of the skill sheets. If there is any docs on what
   a gate crystal is meant to do, I'd love to see them, but it would be even
   better if there was some way to find rumors in Olympia through explore or
   some such. Then there would be a few nobles who had heard of gate crystals,
   there would be others who knew what they did, and still others who had them
   and had to figure out how to use them. The beginning of a quest system.
   Actually, maybe my artifact noble will be helpful. Anyway this is a very
   nice touch."

