subloc/monster seeder:
	create 0-2 sublocs in each province
	seed with a monster

monster seed:
	choose one of the appropriate beasts
	choice:
		0.  no treasure
		1.  some gold
		2.  indep prisoner swear-on-release
		3.  artifact

artifact create:
	1.  some kind of bonus
	2.  require artifact to defeat some monster
	3.  pair or tri artifact in ritual


monster_seed(level):
	choose appropriate level monster

	then:
		0. no treasure
		1. some gold
		2. a quantity of a rare tradegood
		3. indep prisoner swear-on-release
		4. artifact
			a.  member of a ritual group
			b.  required to defeat a monster

	and:
		0. nothing
		1. choose level-1 artifact necessary to defeat


artifact benefit:
	1.  bonus to attack/defense/missile/aura
	2.  no-sick
	3.  undead wipe out
	4.  elfstone

artifact purpose
	1.  required to defeat monster
	2.  member of ritual group


attack/defense/missile/aura/no-sick boost for items
(monster, item) pair such that monster can only be defeated with item
special prisoner flag:  prisoner swears to noble on release

	seed_artifact(art, level)

	select ready sublocs
	seed hardcoded artifacts

	while sublocs remain
		choose a level
		art = make_artifact(level);
		seed_artifact(art, level);



